If your looking for quality breakfast, great customer service at a good price this is the place to go.
My family and I come here at least twice a month, and drive there all the way from Laveen.
Everytime you go there for breakfast they give you a coupon for a buy one get one free breakfast on the way out.
So our breakfast for 2 adults and 2 kids under 6 ends up costing us under $20 bucks.
The chicken friend steak and the steak and eggs are my favorite.

