I started dining here with my mom in early 2012.
The last 3 visits we had over the summer were horrible.
My mom's food was ice cold while mine arrived at the right temperature.
When she asked the waitress for a new plate, she was given an attitude, like she was lying about how hot her food was.
It took awhile for her to get her plate back and since I have good manners and went there to eat WITH my mom, I waited to eat my food until she had hers.
The next two times service was very very slow, and there weren't that many people in the restaurant.
It took over twenty minutes just to order drinks!
While the food is okay, typical diner food, I will not be returning to this establishment due to it's serious lack of customer service.

